---
title: Spiced Chicken & Onion Gravy with Potato Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: Want an easy way to make dinner a little more interesting without having to add a tonne of spices and extra
ingredients? We highly recommend our sweet yet peppery onion gravy to drizzle over the chicken. Soak it up with a
fluffy mashed potato and dinner has reached a new level of tastiness.

